<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1179.101388.figure16>
    dc:description "Figure 16. Cryphalus asperatus A distribution B lateral and dorsal view C aedeagus D SEM, specimen from Calibaba, Romania E SEM (43 x magnification), specimen from Calibaba, Romania." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/903300" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1179.101388.figure17>
    dc:description "Figure 17. Cryphalus saltuarius A distribution B lateral and dorsal view C aedeagus D SEM, specimen from Ostby, Norway E SEM (43 x magnification), specimen from Ostby, Norway." ;
